(2, NULL, 'Suraya Bilkis', 'suraya-bilkis', 'Chairperson', 'A successful organization is driven by a team of quality professionals having honesty, sincerity and dedication to the organization. In Healthcare, we maintain an environment where best people of the industry are working as a team', 'Ms Suraya Bilkis is the chairperson of Healthcare Pharmaceuticals Limited. Her entrepreneurship encompasses Rising Trading Corporation, Kushtia; Soronika Enterprise Kushtia; Healthcare Dairy and Food Products Limited; Healthcare Diagnostic Solutions Limited (HDSL); Healthcare Diagnostic Centre Limited (HDCL); Healthcare Formulations Ltd (HFL); Healthcare Life Science Limited (HLSL). She is a Director in Healthcare Distribution Limited (HDC); Shelaidah Dairy Limited (SD); and Alo Multipurpose Limited.', '<p>A successful organization is driven by a team of quality professionals having honesty, sincerity and dedication to the organization. In Healthcare, we maintain an environment where best people of the industry are working as a team.<br />\r\nSince inception, Healthcare Pharmaceuticals Limited strictly maintains its quality policy established by a panel of Professional and technical experts from home and abroad. We are thankful to Roche experts for their kind advice and assistance to establish such a wonderful manufacturing facility in Bangladesh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HPL is dedicated and passionate to apply innovative ideas in Marketing and manufacturing by availing most modern technology to provide most anticipated products conforming to the global standard of branded generics.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Safety is a major consideration; so HPL follows Environment Health and Safety (EHS) policy to maintain a harmonious relation with neighbors, authorities, customers and suppliers. HPL is committed to enhance EHS awareness and continuously motivates employees on EHS culture through training towards all levels.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>HPL has set principles for product development which provide the best Pharmacokinetic and Pharmacodynamic effects ensuring the utmost efficacy of medicines. HPL is continuously updating and installing advanced technology, in consultation with world renowned experts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wishing all the best to Healthcare family!</p>', NULL, 'Board of Directors', 'suraya-bilkis-2024-10-06-6702548171d50.png', '2024-08-24 09:21:11', '2024-10-06 09:53:57'),
(3, NULL, 'Alauddin Ahmed', 'alauddin-ahmed', 'Managing Director', 'Success of a pharmaceuticals company depends on consistently maintaining the highest standard of quality.', 'Mr. Alauddin Ahmed is the founder of Healthcare Pharmaceuticals Limited. He is also the Managing Director in Healthcare Distribution Company (HDC) and Shelaidah Dairy Ltd. Mr. Ahmed is holding the position of Chairman in Alo Malti-purpose Limited and Bangla Bandha Land Port Limited. Mr. Alauddin Ahmed is well known for his philanthropic work, e.g. establishing schools, colleges, mosques, madrasahs, roads, irrigation facilities, orphanages, hospitals, education park for children, tube wells for safe drinking water etc.', '<p>Success of a pharmaceuticals company depends on consistently maintaining the highest standard of quality. Our commitment to quality encouraged us to establish a world class manufacturing facility conforming to Good Manufacturing Practices (GMP) with the active support and technical guidance of the globally reputed pharmaceuticals company F. Hoffmann- La Roche Limited, Basel, Switzerland.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our mission is to develop and manufacture pharmaceuticals formulations in the most appropriate manner and to ensure the safety, efficacy and usefulness of our products.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We direct our efforts to improve the quality of human life by enabling people to do more, feel better and live with full essence of life.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>By the grace of the Almighty and with the motivation and support of our people and partners, we look forward to be seen as an organization pioneering the implementation of innovative ideas, respected for strict adherence to ethical practices, reputed for the quality of products and appreciated for sustainable growth in our national and global operations.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'Board of Directors', 'alauddin-ahmed-2024-10-06-67025519a0c74.png', '2024-08-24 09:24:01', '2024-10-06 09:54:37'),
(4, NULL, 'Muhammad Halimuzzaman', 'muhammad-halimuzzaman', 'DMD & CEO', 'Product Quality is the cornerstone of our success. It is our constant endeavor to provide quality products & services for customer satisfaction.', 'Mr. Md. Halimuzzaman is the DMD & CEO of Healthcare Pharmaceuticals Ltd (HPL), the fastest growing pharmaceuticals company in Bangladesh with more than 6,000 employees. HPL is manufacturing more than 500 products and has a large sales and distribution network within the country and also overseas markets in Asia, Africa, CIS region, USA, Brazil, EU, Australia etc. \r\n\r\nBesides Healthcare Pharmaceuticals Ltd, Mr. Halimuzzaman also looks after the overall business activities of several sister concerns including Healthcare Life Sciences Ltd.\r\n\r\nHe is a Pharmacist from the University of Dhaka, Bangladesh and an MBA (Major in Finance). Mr. Halimuzzaman has 32 years of professional working experience in different fields of Pharmaceutical industry.\r\n\r\nHe is the Treasurer & Member of the Executive Committee, Bangladesh Association of Pharmaceuticals Industries (BAPI) and the Member of Bangladesh Pharmaceutical Society (BPS). He is an integral part of several government delegations on pharmaceutical sector development in foreign countries and represents BAPI in the formulation of fiscal policy on Pharmaceuticals Industry in Bangladesh. Being a Director of Bangladesh Economic Zone Investors Association (BEZIA), he is working for the protection of common interest of all members/investors and for contributing to the economic success of Bangladesh. \r\n\r\nMr. Halimuzzaman is the Sr. Vice President of BAAS, an alumni of Association for Overseas Technical Scholarship and Sustainable Partnership (AOTS) works under the Ministry of Economy, Trade & Industry, Japan.', '<p>Product Quality is the cornerstone of our success. It is our constant endeavor to provide quality products &amp; services for highest level of customer satisfaction.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our dedicated team has a shared commitment to collaboration and innovation as well as scientific and business excellence. We are excited to move forward to our mission to deliver meaningful therapies to the patients of every corner of the world.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I would like to thank to all Physicians and Medical Practitioners patronizing to Healthcare Pharmaceuticals Limited through prescribing products as well as sharing their valuable feedback for further development.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We are spirally moving forward to introduce our products globally. As a part of our global endeavors, we are now exporting our products to different countries in Asia, Africa and CIS region, whereas in many countries&rsquo; products are under registration process.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Key strengths driving our company&rsquo;s growth are dedicated teams energized by strategic thinking, innovation, ethics, values, management excellence and customer service orientation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Finally, while I talk about brands, products and manufacturing facilities, I strongly believe that, the driving force behind Healthcare Pharmaceuticals Limited is, its people. &nbsp;The organization continues to focus on getting the best people on board and provide them the most conducive environment, where they can grow and unleash their potential; at the same time contribute to the wellbeing of people and ensure patients comfort and benefits.</p>', NULL, 'Board of Directors', 'muhammad-halimuzzaman-2024-10-06-67025587d9474.png', '2024-08-24 09:28:10', '2024-10-06 09:55:41'),
