(8, NULL, '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>HPL&rsquo;s Quality Unit operates in accordance with WHO guidelines, comprising the independent Quality Assurance department and the Quality Council.</strong> Together, they ensure comprehensive quality management for medicinal products. The Quality Assurance department includes Quality Control and Quality Compliance, focusing on activities that impact product quality. This system guarantees that products meet required standards through Good Manufacturing Practices (GMP) and ongoing quality improvements.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-09-23 11:26:56', 'Quality Management System', '', 'default.png'),
