(86, '20', 'Can Cefuroxime (Furotil) be used during pregnancy and lactation?', 'Cefuroxime is classified as a Pregnancy Category B drug by the US FDA. There are no well-controlled studies in pregnant women, so it should only be used if clearly needed. Cefuroxime is excreted in human milk, so caution should be exercised when administering it to nursing mothers.', 'can-cefuroxime-furotil-be-used-during-pregnancy-and-lactation', NULL, '2024-10-08 16:33:02', '2024-10-08 16:33:02'),
