(90, '20', 'What precautions should be taken while using Cefuroxime (Furotil)?', 'Cefuroxime should be used cautiously in patients receiving potent diuretics and those with a history of colitis. While cephalosporins can generally be administered to penicillin-sensitive patients, there is some risk of cross-reactivity. Furotil should also be used carefully in patients with impaired renal function.', 'what-precautions-should-be-taken-while-using-cefuroxime-furotil', NULL, '2024-10-08 16:34:07', '2024-10-08 16:34:07'),
