(36, 'Instruction', NULL, 'Instruction', NULL, '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#0070c0\">For online registration of 78 th DMC day ,2023 celebration program</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">*You have to be a DMCan (current MBBS course student of DMC or who completed MBBS from DMC) </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">*If your spouse is also a DMCan, both of you need to register separately and one of you can mention regarding kids. </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">*If you are a life member of DMC alumni trust, please enter your LM No (life member list with LM No is attached in the Membership section of our website) </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">*During registration process, please fill up every required field mentioned in the form correctly. You can complete your online payment by any mobile banking or by Visa/Master/Nexus card.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">*After successful completion of your registration, you will get an e-ticket on your mail. Take a printed copy of this e-ticket and preserve it on your mobile for DMC day celebration program.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">*Online registration will be continued up to 20 th June,2023.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">*For any problem regarding online payment, please contact -01783487160,01620116337.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">*Registration by any non DMCan (giving false information) will be cancelled without any refunding.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#0070c0\">N.B. DMC alumni trust Will preserve the right of any change, correction or new addition regarding registration process if necessary.</span></span></strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">For offline registration contact with DMC alumni trust office</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"> -</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Office room -413(3rd floor), Dhaka Medical College, Dhaka-1000.</span></span></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Mobile: 01783487160, 01620116337</span></span></span></p>', '', '2023-05-29 11:57:47', '2023-05-31 14:51:07'),
