(96, 21, 'Side Effects', 'side-effects', '<p>Adverse effects to Furotil have occurred infrequently and have been generally mild and transient in nature. Effects reported include rashes and gastrointestinal disturbances. As with other antibiotics, prolonged use may result in the overgrowth of non susceptible organisms e.g. Candida.</p>', NULL, 'dafault.png', '2024-10-08 16:24:13', '2024-10-08 16:24:13'),
