(9, 'Quality POLICY', NULL, 'quality-policy', NULL, 'To preserve and improve patient health by consistently delivering high quality, safe and effective specialty pharmaceutical products and services, that meet or exceed customer expectations. All associates of Healthcare Pharmaceuticals are committed to successfully deploying our company\'s Quality Policy to all aspects of our activities - assuring continued high quality, usefulness and effectiveness of products for our customers. Quality and Customers orientation are a company commitment and the shared responsibility of all associates. This commitment will be maintained through having the competent people doing the right things, the first time, every time. We are assuring continued high quality through state of the art technology, which develops and commercializes safe pharmaceutical products that enhance the quality of life. We are having an experienced workforce, equipped with continuing education and training in emerging Quality techniques and philosophy. We are having a management team that is accountable for effective review and support of quality, through the prioritization, resourcing, and timely execution of quality-conscious decision-making. Confirmation of our success based upon the testimony of our customers, regulators, business partners, and employees.', NULL, NULL, '2024-08-27 04:12:11', '2024-08-27 04:14:05'),
(10, 'EHS Policy', NULL, 'ehs-policy', NULL, '<ul>\r\n	<li>To become one of the leading companies with regard to Environment, Health and Safety performance</li>\r\n	<li>Committed to increase awareness and motivate employees on EHS culture through training at all levels</li>\r\n	<li>To respect local laws and regulations to conduct EHS activities</li>\r\n	<li>Committed to provide a safe and healthy working environment to ensure the health and safety of our employees, contractors, visitors and neighbors</li>\r\n	<li>To avoid all the risks related to occupation by identifying and evaluating in time and take necessary preventive measures at an early stage</li>\r\n	<li>To identify all environmental hazards utilizing qualitative and quantitative analysis, assess and reduce the corresponding risk to an acceptable level</li>\r\n	<li>To identify and assess potential exposure to chemical, physical and biological stressors utilizing qualitative and / or quantitative evaluation</li>\r\n	<li>To ensure continuous development of EHS standards</li>\r\n	<li>To maintain good relation on EHS issues with neighbors, authorities, customers and suppliers.</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, NULL, '2024-08-27 04:12:51', '2024-09-15 11:32:59'),
(11, 'ISMS POLICY', NULL, 'isms-policy', NULL, 'Healthcare Pharmaceuticals Ltd. is one ofthe leading pharmaceutical companies in Bangladesh, having been certified by the international pharmaceutical regulatory authorities, which started its commercial operation in 1988 as a Pharmaceuticals Company. All the information systems and operations of the oiganizations are managed through the IT service, and the IT sector is one of the most susceptible .\"\"to.s in the prospect of Information Security because of the nature and value of the business it executes using Information Technology, Healthcare Pharmaceuticals is focused on the challenges to its lnformation hssets. Healthcare PharmaceutiCals Limited realizes the importance of legal compliance with the prevailing local laws, rules, and regulations, as well as the globally agreed standards, rules, and regulations that are applicable to its Information Security Manalement System. With this agenda, Healthcare Pharmaceuticals strives to aqhieve Information Security Management System pe.for-ance that fulfills the applicable requirements satisffing the needs and expectations of its Interested Parties and continually improving to protect its Information assets. To achieve the desired goal of ensuring the Confidentiality, Integrity, and Availability of its information asset, Healthcare Pharmaceuticals has initiated and implemented an Information Security Management System (ISMS) in the organization. Healthcare Pharmaceuticals Limited is committed to fulfilling all the legal and other requirements which are applicable to its Information Security Management System on an ongoing basis. This policy is endorsed by the top-level management of Healthcare Pharmaceuticals Limited and communicated to all parties relevant to its Information Security.', NULL, NULL, '2024-08-27 04:13:19', '2024-08-27 04:13:19');
